                        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-gray-500 transition-transform duration-300 transform" id="icon-pillar-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <div class="accordion-content p-6 text-gray-600 hidden" id="content-pillar-1">
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">Current State:</h4>
                        <p class="mb-4">Limited automation; primarily manual code scans with few integrations into CI/CD pipelines.</p>
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">Recommendations:</h4>
                        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
                            <li>Integrate SAST and DAST tools directly into CI/CD workflows to enable automated security scans on every build.</li>
                            <li>Automate dependency scanning to identify and patch vulnerable libraries.</li>
                            <li>Implement Infrastructure as Code (IaC) security scanning to prevent misconfigurations.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="border rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
                    <div class="accordion-header flex justify-between items-center p-6 bg-gray-50 hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors" onclick="toggleAccordion('pillar-2')">
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700">2. Threat Modeling & Design Review</h3>
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-gray-500 transition-transform duration-300 transform" id="icon-pillar-2" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <div class="accordion-content p-6 text-gray-600 hidden" id="content-pillar-2">
                         <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">Current State:</h4>
                        <p class="mb-4">Ad-hoc and infrequent threat modeling, often after development is complete.</p>
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">Recommendations:</h4>
                        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
                            <li>Introduce formal threat modeling into the early stages of the Software Development Life Cycle (SDLC).</li>
                            <li>Conduct regular design reviews with security experts to identify design flaws.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="border rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
                    <div class="accordion-header flex justify-between items-center p-6 bg-gray-50 hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors" onclick="toggleAccordion('pillar-3')">
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700">3. Security Culture & Training</h3>
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-gray-500 transition-transform duration-300 transform" id="icon-pillar-3" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <div class="accordion-content p-6 text-gray-600 hidden" id="content-pillar-3">
                         <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">Current State:</h4>
                        <p class="mb-4">Security is seen as a separate function, not a shared responsibility.</p>
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">Recommendations:</h4>
                        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
                            <li>Launch a formal DevSecOps training program for all development teams.</li>
                            <li>Establish security champions within each team to act as liaisons.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="report-section">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6 border-b-2 pb-2">Priority Roadmap</h2>
            <div class="roadmap-timeline">
                <div class="roadmap-item">
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-xl text-gray-800 mb-1">Phase 1: Foundational (0-3 Months)</h3>
                    <ul class="list-disc pl-5 text-gray-600 space-y-1">
                        <li>Implement a dedicated SAST tool for static code analysis.</li>
                        <li>Automate dependency scanning in the CI pipeline.</li>
                        <li>Conduct initial DevSecOps training for key teams.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="roadmap-item">
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-xl text-gray-800 mb-1">Phase 2: Integration (3-9 Months)</h3>
                    <ul class="list-disc pl-5 text-gray-600 space-y-1">
                        <li>Integrate DAST for dynamic application security testing.</li>
                        <li>Begin formal threat modeling exercises for all new projects.</li>
                        <li>Establish metrics and KPIs for security findings.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="roadmap-item">
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-xl text-gray-800 mb-1">Phase 3: Optimization (9-18 Months)</h3>
                    <ul class="list-disc pl-5 text-gray-600 space-y-1">
                        <li>Implement automated security gating and policy enforcement.</li>
                        <li>Introduce chaos engineering to test security controls.</li>
                        <li>Roll out a formal bug bounty program.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="report-section">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6 border-b-2 pb-2">Tools Suggestions</h2>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm flex flex-col items-center text-center">
                    <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                        <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-blue-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2l4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="font-semibold text-xl text-gray-800 mb-2">SAST Tool (e.g., SonarQube)</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">Performs static analysis of source code to find vulnerabilities early in the development cycle.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm flex flex-col items-center text-center">
                    <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                        <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-green-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="font-semibold text-xl text-gray-800 mb-2">DAST Tool (e.g., OWASP ZAP)</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">Analyzes web applications in a running state to find security flaws like injection attacks.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm flex flex-col items-center text-center">
                    <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-yellow-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                        <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-yellow-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4m0 4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="font-semibold text-xl text-gray-800 mb-2">SCA Tool (e.g., Snyk)</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">Identifies open-source vulnerabilities and license compliance issues in application dependencies.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
